@Reasoning:
Verifies the parser handles a directive with an argument (.globl
main). Catches a regression where the parser expects directives to
be standalone or expects different argument grammar.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation:
Tokenize ".globl main", parse -> ast. Assert ast not null.
@End Implementation

@TestCases:
- ".globl main" -> non-null directive AST, passed
- Parser rejects argument -> ast == 0 -> "Directive parsed" fails
